==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fleeced
<hw>Fleeced</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Furnished
with a fleece; <as>as, a sheep is well <ex>fleeced</ex></as>.</def>
<rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Stripped of a fleece; plundered; robbed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fleeceless</ent>⟦br⟧
